### Logging/Tracing Requirements

```rust
use tracing::{debug, trace, instrument};

impl Router {
    #[instrument(level = "debug", skip(self, handler))]
    pub fn register_tool_with_icon(&mut self, handler: impl ToolHandler) {
        let icon = handler.icon();
        debug!(
            name = %handler.name(),
            has_icon = icon.is_some(),
            icon_src = ?icon.map(|i| i.src.as_deref()),
            "Registering tool"
        );
    }
}

// In macro expansion
trace!(icon_attr = ?attr, "Parsing icon attribute in tool macro");
```

Required trace points:
- `DEBUG`: Tool/resource/prompt registration with icon info
- `TRACE`: Icon attribute parsing in macros
- `DEBUG`: Icon serialization in list responses

